2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new network architecture for image segmentation tasks. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is likely as the paper proposes a new approach to handle the complexity of natural images. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is likely as the paper proposes a new network architecture that iteratively combines features from different resolution scales. 
5. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as semantic segmentation.
